date: Sun Feb 06 2022 01:22:00 GMT+1100 (Australian Eastern Daylight Time)
description: Victory beat Melbourne City 2-0 in the final round of the Australian Football League. The result was the first time the two teams had met in the competition. Victory's win means they will be the first team to win the tournament in Australia's history of the tournament. It is the second time the team has won the competition in a row over the past two years.
topicText: WATCH: Melbourne Victory crowned FFA Cup 2021 Winners Melbourne Victory are FFA Cup Winners for a second time after defeating Central Coast Mariners 2-1 at AAMI Park on Saturday night. Football Australia tonight confirmed that from the 2022 edition onwards, Australia's largest national knockout football competition will be played as the ... FFA Cup to be renamed Australia Cup The FFA Cup knockout competition will be renamed the Australia Cup from the 2022 edition. Saturday's 2021 FFA Cup final between Melbourne Victory and ... Davidson blasts Victory to FFA Cup glory Melbourne Victory have won the FFA Cup after a stunning free kick from Jason Davidson put them on the road to success in the final. Victory beat Mariners for FFA Cup glory Melbourne Victory have their first trophy under Tony Popovic in a FFA Cup win over Central Coast. Ten months after he was charged with lifting Melbourne Victory out of the doldrums, Tony Popovic's revolution has delivered its first trophy ... Popovic delights in Victory FFA Cup glory Melbourne Victory have the first trophy of their revival under coach Tony Popovic, claiming the FFA Cup final with a 2-1 win over Central Coast. FFA Cup to become Australia Cup From 2022 onwards, Australia's largest national knockout football men's competition will be known as the Australia Cup.
